These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, metal
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of metal is not to the right of the fan of metal##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | metal | techno |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, zombie
1. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching drama movies is not to the left of the person watching zombie movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | drama |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: dog, snake
1. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
2. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
3. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the owner of the dog##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | dog | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, bike
1. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | airplane | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-5::.
